posts.description:
We have the perfect DIY up on the blog to get stuck in this weekend (especially  for our friends in the Southern Hemisphere where it's getting cooler)...... Dyeing sheepskins! Maybe yours is looking tired and a little worse for wear or you want to co ordinate a new colour scheme.
------ our DIY handmade home contributor @keeniediy has all the tips and tricks on how to, link in profile.
📷 @keeniediy #eclecticcreative #diy #handmade
Gorgeous west village style apartment ready for sale for @theurbanstylist // #melbre #propertystyling #homestaging

Peg and I have been feeling massively uninspired with @instagram lately. She's over it and wants me to pull the plug, but that's too extreme. 🙋🏽
...... I'd love to know how you're feeling and whether you feel similar? I'd also love to know what you want to see on my feed, all the work you see on here is mine unless otherwise stated 💫 ......
You can see me and my big talking head in the stories, let me know how you're feeling. 🌿🔮 ...... and update. Have you heard of #shadowban Instagrams new war on engagement. They've banned this post. Google it 🤛🏼#eclecticcreative

🙏🏼 Lest we forget ..... I am here living my life free because of you. The ultimate sacrifice ❤
📷 @flowersvasette #lestweforget #anzacday

Do you have cute prints or cards that desperately need frames but can't find the right size? // .......
Our new contributor @shethemaker has created these contemporary oak chain frames - perfect for your home and she shows us how! Part of our Crafty + Creative segment, Amanda will contributing smart and savvy DIYs and life hacks. Full details on the blog 👍🏼 📷 @shethemaker #eclecticcreative

Attention Perth Australia peeps! I'm going to be heading to the gorgeous west coast city, Perth in a few weeks for work and some overdue family time. It's been 5 years since I moved to Melbourne... so much would have changed - tag your favourite Perth brands and businesses I need to visit! #eclecticcreative #perth #perthisok
---- Interiors by me 📷 @theroomilluminated

I'm dreaming of "escaping", it's the Pisces in me 🐠 .... not running away but ducking off to the unknown, the unfamiliar.... I'm the type of person who thrives on change I've come to realise // We are coming up to 5 years in Melbourne and 2 years in this current home. I feel that change is on the horizon 🌿
...... I just don't know what or where yet, but I know it's coming and embrace it wholeheartedly. Do you ever get like this? ....... so for now a studio rearrange is on the cards. Bring in some new energy, fresh air and clear thoughts. Happy Saturday 🙏🏼💕 #eclecticcreative #workspacie #pocketofmyhome

I'll be seeing you again soon Bendigo 👋🏼 .... another road trip in 2 weeks! Where should I go? Who should I go meet? Tag your local Bendigo small businesses below 🌿👇🏼 @explorebendigo #explorebendigo #bendigo #eclecticcreative

If you need help pulling together a scheme for your interior project (yes it can be very daunting can't it?) - be it the soft furnishings, paint, timber or fittings and fixtures - I would love to help guide you. -----This is one of my favourite things to work on with my clients - I've been told on several accounts I have an uncanny gift for colour and pattern - and have since I was a child. 🙊 Doo nooo nooo nooo 💫
---------
We can go relaxed, refreshed, classic or colourful, let's start this journey together and create a custom scheme especially for you // hit up Colour Consults via my website for further info 👋🏼 #eclecticcreative

Back in March, I hit the road ( 3 hours north of Melbourne) to celebrate my birthday at @cactuscountry | I've got a new segment on the blog, Designer Road Trip | sometimes all you need is to put a little distance between you and what's familiar and you're immediately inspired -----------🚗💨💨💨💨💨
| blog post about the incredible Cactus Country, up now - link in profile. 🌵 #eclecticcreative
